HEADWORD: Immane
<hw>Im*mane"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>immanis</ets>.]</ety> <def>Very great; huge; vast; also, monstrous
in character; inhuman; atrocious; fierce.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧So <xex>immane</xex> a man.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Chapman.</au></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Im*mane"ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms></p>

